<p>Hi <%= @resource.name.presence || @resource.email %>,</p>

<p>You've been invited to PRESENT — a group management app your admin uses to track attendance and finances.</p>

<p>Click the link below to set your password and activate your account:</p>

<p><%= link_to "Activate my account", edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token) %></p>

<p>This link expires in 7 days. If you were not expecting this invitation, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
